description: Usage reference for ask-cursor.mjs
alwaysApply: false
globs: "**/*.{ts,js,py,md,json}"
---

```bash
node .claude/skills/omega-cursor-cli/scripts/ask-cursor.mjs "PROMPT" [--model MODEL] [--json] [--yolo] [--trust] [--approve-mcps] [--sandbox] [--timeout-ms N]
```

- `--json` maps to `cursor-agent --output-format json`.
- `--yolo` maps to `cursor-agent --yolo`. Auto-approves all tool calls for fully non-interactive pipelines.
- `--trust` maps to `cursor-agent --trust`. Suppresses workspace permission prompts in headless environments.
- `--approve-mcps` maps to `cursor-agent --approve-mcps`. Automatically approves MCP server connections.
- `--sandbox` is a **deprecated** alias for `--yolo`. Will be removed in a future version.